<center><b><font face="Arial,Helvetica"><font color="#FFFFFF"><font size=+1>THE
THYLACINE IN CAPTIVITY:</font></font></font></b>
<br><font face="Arial,Helvetica"><font color="#FFFFFF"><font size=+1>-
<i>BENJAMIN</i>:
THE LAST KNOWN CAPTIVE THYLACINE -</font></font></font>
<br><font face="Arial,Helvetica"><font color="#FFFFFF">(page 1)</font></font></center>
</td>
</tr>
</table></center>
<font color="#999999">.</font></td>
</tr>
